(PROGN
 (PROGN
  (EVAL-WHEN (:COMPILE-TOPLEVEL :LOAD-TOPLEVEL :EXECUTE)
    (APPLY 'UIOP/PACKAGE:ENSURE-PACKAGE
           '(:%NUKLEAR :NICKNAMES (:%NK) :DOCUMENTATION NIL :USE NIL :SHADOW
             NIL :SHADOWING-IMPORT-FROM NIL :IMPORT-FROM NIL :EXPORT NIL
             :INTERN NIL :RECYCLE (:%NUKLEAR :%NK) :MIX NIL :REEXPORT NIL
             :UNINTERN NIL))))
 (PROGN
  (EVAL-WHEN (:COMPILE-TOPLEVEL :LOAD-TOPLEVEL :EXECUTE)
    (SETQ CLAW::*FAILED-WRAPS* NIL)
    (LET ((CLAW::*FOREIGN-RECORD-INDEX* (MAKE-HASH-TABLE)))
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::INT8-T "int8_t" ':CHAR)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::INT16-T "int16_t" ':SHORT)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::INT32-T "int32_t" ':INT)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::UINT8-T "uint8_t" ':UNSIGNED-CHAR)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::UINT16-T "uint16_t"
                                  ':UNSIGNED-SHORT)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::UINT32-T "uint32_t"
                                  ':UNSIGNED-INT)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR::UINTPTR-T "uintptr_t"
                                  ':UNSIGNED-LONG)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:CHAR "nk_char" '%NUKLEAR::INT8-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:UCHAR "nk_uchar"
                                  '%NUKLEAR::UINT8-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:BYTE "nk_byte" '%NUKLEAR::UINT8-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:SHORT "nk_short"
                                  '%NUKLEAR::INT16-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:USHORT "nk_ushort"

      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:INT "nk_int" '%NUKLEAR::INT32-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:UINT "nk_uint" '%NUKLEAR::UINT32-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:SIZE "nk_size"
                                  '%NUKLEAR::UINTPTR-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:PTR "nk_ptr" '%NUKLEAR::UINTPTR-T)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:HASH "nk_hash" '%NUKLEAR:UINT)
      (CLAW::DEFINE-FOREIGN-ALIAS '%NUKLEAR:FLAGS "nk_flags" '%NUKLEAR:UINT)

                                      :BIT-OFFSET 1504 :BIT-ALIGNMENT 32)

                                      :BIT-SIZE 41536 :BIT-OFFSET 1536
                                      :BIT-ALIGNMENT 32)))

       %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-RECT-OUTLINE+ %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-RECT-SOLID+
       %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-CIRCLE-OUTLINE+ %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-CIRCLE-SOLID+
       %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-UNDERSCORE+ %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-X+ %NUKLEAR:+SYMBOL-NONE+
       %NUKLEAR:+TREE-TAB+ %NUKLEAR:+TREE-NODE+ %NUKLEAR:+STATIC+
       %NUKLEAR:+DYNAMIC+ %NUKLEAR:+POPUP-DYNAMIC+ %NUKLEAR:+POPUP-STATIC+
       %NUKLEAR:+RGBA+ %NUKLEAR:+RGB+ %NUKLEAR:+CHART-CLICKED+
       %NUKLEAR:+CHART-HOVERING+ %NUKLEAR:+CHART-MAX+ %NUKLEAR:+CHART-COLUMN+
       %NUKLEAR:+CHART-LINES+ %NUKLEAR:+SHOWN+ %NUKLEAR:+HIDDEN+
       %NUKLEAR:+MAXIMIZED+ %NUKLEAR:+MINIMIZED+ %NUKLEAR:+HORIZONTAL+
       %NUKLEAR:+VERTICAL+ %NUKLEAR:+MODIFIABLE+ %NUKLEAR:+FIXED+
       %NUKLEAR:+BUTTON-REPEATER+ %NUKLEAR:+BUTTON-DEFAULT+ %NUKLEAR:+LEFT+
       %NUKLEAR:+DOWN+ %NUKLEAR:+RIGHT+ %NUKLEAR:+UP+ %NUKLEAR:+TRUE+
       %NUKLEAR:+FALSE+)
     #<PACKAGE "%NUKLEAR">)
    (EXPORT
     '(%NUKLEAR:WINDOW-FLAGS %NUKLEAR:PANEL-ROW-LAYOUT-TYPE %NUKLEAR:PANEL-SET
       %NUKLEAR:PANEL-TYPE %NUKLEAR:STYLE-HEADER-ALIGN %NUKLEAR:STYLE-ITEM-TYPE
       %NUKLEAR:DRAW-VERTEX-LAYOUT-FORMAT %NUKLEAR:DRAW-VERTEX-LAYOUT-ATTRIBUTE
       %NUKLEAR:DRAW-LIST-STROKE %NUKLEAR:DRAW-INDEX %NUKLEAR:COMMAND-CLIPPING
       %NUKLEAR:COMMAND-CUSTOM-CALLBACK %NUKLEAR:COMMAND-TYPE
       %NUKLEAR:TEXT-EDIT-MODE %NUKLEAR:TEXT-EDIT-TYPE
       %NUKLEAR:BUFFER-ALLOCATION-TYPE %NUKLEAR:ALLOCATION-TYPE
       %NUKLEAR:FONT-ATLAS-FORMAT %NUKLEAR:FONT-COORD-TYPE
       %NUKLEAR:QUERY-FONT-GLYPH-F %NUKLEAR:TEXT-WIDTH-F %NUKLEAR:STYLE-CURSOR
       %NUKLEAR:STYLE-COLORS %NUKLEAR:EDIT-EVENTS %NUKLEAR:EDIT-TYPES
       %NUKLEAR:EDIT-FLAGS %NUKLEAR:TEXT-ALIGNMENT %NUKLEAR:TEXT-ALIGN
       %NUKLEAR:WIDGET-STATES %NUKLEAR:WIDGET-LAYOUT-STATES
       %NUKLEAR:PANEL-FLAGS %NUKLEAR:CONVERT-RESULT %NUKLEAR:ANTI-ALIASING
       %NUKLEAR:BUTTONS %NUKLEAR:KEYS %NUKLEAR:SYMBOL-TYPE %NUKLEAR:PLUGIN-COPY
       %NUKLEAR:PLUGIN-PASTE %NUKLEAR:PLUGIN-FILTER %NUKLEAR:PLUGIN-FREE
       %NUKLEAR:PLUGIN-ALLOC %NUKLEAR:TREE-TYPE %NUKLEAR:LAYOUT-FORMAT
       %NUKLEAR:POPUP-TYPE %NUKLEAR:COLOR-FORMAT %NUKLEAR:CHART-EVENT
       %NUKLEAR:CHART-TYPE %NUKLEAR:SHOW-STATES %NUKLEAR:COLLAPSE-STATES
       %NUKLEAR:ORIENTATION %NUKLEAR:MODIFY %NUKLEAR:BUTTON-BEHAVIOR
       %NUKLEAR:HEADING %NUKLEAR:GLYPH %NUKLEAR:RUNE %NUKLEAR:FLAGS
       %NUKLEAR:HASH %NUKLEAR:PTR %NUKLEAR:SIZE %NUKLEAR:UINT %NUKLEAR:INT
       %NUKLEAR:USHORT %NUKLEAR:SHORT %NUKLEAR:BYTE %NUKLEAR:UCHAR
       %NUKLEAR:CHAR)
     #<PACKAGE "%NUKLEAR">))
  (EVAL-WHEN (:LOAD-TOPLEVEL :EXECUTE)
    (CLAW::REPORT-WRAP-FAILURES 'CLAW::LOAD-TIME *STANDARD-OUTPUT*)
    (CLAW::CLEAR-WRAP-FAILURES)))
 (PROGN
  (EVAL-WHEN (:COMPILE-TOPLEVEL :EXECUTE)
    (SB-PCL::COMPILE-OR-LOAD-DEFGENERIC 'CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER))
  (EVAL-WHEN (:LOAD-TOPLEVEL)
    (SB-PCL::LOAD-DEFMETHOD 'STANDARD-METHOD 'CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER 'NIL
                            (LIST (SB-MOP:INTERN-EQL-SPECIALIZER :%NUKLEAR)
                                  (FIND-CLASS 'T))
                            '(PACKAGE-NAME CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH &OPTIONAL
                                           CLAW::LOADER)
                            (LIST* :FUNCTION
                                   (LET* ((SB-PCL::FMF
                                           (SB-INT:NAMED-LAMBDA (SB-PCL::FAST-METHOD
                                                                 CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER
                                                                 ((EQL
                                                                   :%NUKLEAR)
                                                                  T))
                                               (SB-PCL::.PV.
                                                SB-PCL::.NEXT-METHOD-CALL.
                                                PACKAGE-NAME CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH
                                                &OPTIONAL CLAW::LOADER)
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (IGNORABLE SB-PCL::.PV.
                                               SB-PCL::.NEXT-METHOD-CALL.)
                                              (DISABLE-PACKAGE-LOCKS
                                               SB-PCL::PV-ENV-ENVIRONMENT))
                                             (DECLARE (IGNORE PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (SB-PCL::%PARAMETER
                                               CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (SB-PCL::%PARAMETER PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (TYPE T CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (IGNORABLE CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH
                                               PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (SYMBOL-MACROLET ((SB-PCL::PV-ENV-ENVIRONMENT
                                                                SB-PCL::DEFAULT))
                                               (FLET ((NEXT-METHOD-P ()
                                                        (DECLARE
                                                         (OPTIMIZE
                                                          (SB-C:INSERT-STEP-CONDITIONS
                                                           0)))
                                                        (NOT
                                                         (NULL
                                                          SB-PCL::.NEXT-METHOD-CALL.))))
                                                 (DECLARE
                                                  (IGNORABLE
                                                   (FUNCTION NEXT-METHOD-P)))
                                                 (LET ()
                                                   (LET* ((SB-PCL::.ARGS-TAIL.
                                                           NIL)
                                                          (SB-PCL::.DUMMY0.))
                                                     (DECLARE
                                                      (IGNORABLE
                                                       SB-PCL::.ARGS-TAIL.
                                                       SB-PCL::.DUMMY0.))
                                                     (LOCALLY
                                                      (DECLARE
                                                       (DISABLE-PACKAGE-LOCKS
                                                        SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED))
                                                      (SYMBOL-MACROLET ((SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED
                                                                         (QUOTE)))
                                                        (DECLARE
                                                         (ENABLE-PACKAGE-LOCKS
                                                          SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED))
                                                        (BLOCK
                                                            CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER
                                                          (CLAW::WRITE-C-LIBRARY-IMPLEMENTATION
                                                           CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH
                                                           (CLAW::PATH-OR-ASDF
                                                            '"bodge_nuklear.h")
                                                           (CLAW::PACKAGE-FUNCTIONS
                                                            :%NUKLEAR)
                                                           CLAW::LOADER))))))))))
                                          (SB-PCL::MF
                                           (SB-PCL::%MAKE-METHOD-FUNCTION
                                            SB-PCL::FMF)))
                                     (SB-MOP:SET-FUNCALLABLE-INSTANCE-FUNCTION
                                      SB-PCL::MF
                                      (SB-PCL::METHOD-FUNCTION-FROM-FAST-FUNCTION
                                       SB-PCL::FMF '(:ARG-INFO (2 . T))))
                                     SB-PCL::MF)
                                   '(SB-PCL::PLIST (:ARG-INFO (2 . T))
                                     SB-PCL::SIMPLE-NEXT-METHOD-CALL T))
                            (SB-C:SOURCE-LOCATION)))
  (EVAL-WHEN (:EXECUTE)
    (SB-PCL::LOAD-DEFMETHOD 'STANDARD-METHOD 'CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER 'NIL
                            (LIST (SB-MOP:INTERN-EQL-SPECIALIZER :%NUKLEAR)
                                  (FIND-CLASS 'T))
                            '(PACKAGE-NAME CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH &OPTIONAL
                                           CLAW::LOADER)
                            (LIST* :FUNCTION
                                   (LET* ((SB-PCL::FMF

                                                                 CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER

                                                PACKAGE-NAME CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH
                                                &OPTIONAL CLAW::LOADER)
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (IGNORABLE SB-PCL::.PV.
                                               SB-PCL::.NEXT-METHOD-CALL.)
                                              (DISABLE-PACKAGE-LOCKS
                                               SB-PCL::PV-ENV-ENVIRONMENT))
                                             (DECLARE (IGNORE PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (SB-PCL::%PARAMETER
                                               CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (SB-PCL::%PARAMETER PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (TYPE T CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH))
                                             (DECLARE
                                              (IGNORABLE CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH
                                               PACKAGE-NAME))
                                             (SYMBOL-MACROLET ((SB-PCL::PV-ENV-ENVIRONMENT
                                                                SB-PCL::DEFAULT))
                                               (FLET ((NEXT-METHOD-P ()
                                                        (DECLARE
                                                         (OPTIMIZE
                                                          (SB-C:INSERT-STEP-CONDITIONS
                                                           0)))
                                                        (NOT
                                                         (NULL
                                                          SB-PCL::.NEXT-METHOD-CALL.))))
                                                 (DECLARE

                                                   (FUNCTION NEXT-METHOD-P)))
                                                 (LET ()
                                                   (LET* ((SB-PCL::.ARGS-TAIL.
                                                           NIL)
                                                          (SB-PCL::.DUMMY0.))
                                                     (DECLARE
                                                      (IGNORABLE
                                                       SB-PCL::.ARGS-TAIL.
                                                       SB-PCL::.DUMMY0.))
                                                     (LOCALLY
                                                      (DECLARE

                                                        SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED))
                                                      (SYMBOL-MACROLET ((SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED
                                                                         (QUOTE)))
                                                        (DECLARE

                                                          SB-PCL::%PARAMETER-BINDING-MODIFIED))
                                                        (BLOCK
                                                            CLAW:DUMP-C-WRAPPER
                                                          (CLAW::WRITE-C-LIBRARY-IMPLEMENTATION
                                                           CLAW::WRAPPER-PATH

                                                            '"bodge_nuklear.h")
                                                           (CLAW::PACKAGE-FUNCTIONS
                                                            :%NUKLEAR)
                                                           CLAW::LOADER))))))))))
                                          (SB-PCL::MF
                                           (SB-PCL::%MAKE-METHOD-FUNCTION
                                            SB-PCL::FMF)))
                                     (SB-MOP:SET-FUNCALLABLE-INSTANCE-FUNCTION
                                      SB-PCL::MF

                                       SB-PCL::FMF '(:ARG-INFO (2 . T))))
                                     SB-PCL::MF)

                                     SB-PCL::SIMPLE-NEXT-METHOD-CALL T))
                            (SB-C:SOURCE-LOCATION)))))
